Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.waters.plain.base.Element
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Proxy
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractNamedElement, EdgeElement, ExpressionElement, GeometryElement, GraphElement, GuardActionBlockElement, TraceElement, TraceStepElement, TransitionElement, VariableMarkingElement

    public abstract class Element
extends Object
implements Proxy, Cloneable, Serializable

    The common base class for all Waters elements in the plain implementation.

    This is the abstract base class of all non-aggregrate Waters elements in the plain implementation. It provides the basic functionality of an immutable object.

    Author:
    Robi Malik
